'''德卢瓦猿'''（{{lang-en|De Loys' Ape}}，旧译：德洛巨猿）是指[[地质学|地质学家]]{{link-fr|弗朗索瓦·德·卢瓦|François de Loys}}于1920年在[[哥伦比亚|哥伦比亚]]与[[委內瑞拉|委内瑞拉]]边境[[塔拉河_(哥伦比亚)|塔拉河]]发现的神秘[[灵长目|灵长类]]动物。目前关于德卢瓦猿普遍认为是[[蜘蛛猴|蜘蛛猴]]误认或为一场骗局。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/tetrapod-zoology/de-loys-8217-ape-and-what-to-do-with-it/|title=De Loys’ Ape and what to do with it|accessdate=2017-06-30|author=Darren Naish|archive-date=2017-04-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170403200345/https://blogs.scientificamerican.com/tetrapod-zoology/de-loys-8217-ape-and-what-to-do-with-it/|dead-url=no}}</ref>

== 目击 ==
1920年，地质学家弗朗索瓦·德·卢瓦及其队伍在塔拉河遭遇两只约1.57米高的怪猿。由于怪猿意图攻击探险队，探险队随之开枪还击，击毙雌猿，雄负伤脱逃。之后探险队对雌猿进行摄像并开始拨皮，意图留下皮毛和头骨，但因种种原因仅有一张照片留存。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidbressan/2016/01/31/de-loys-ape-was-a-well-played-anthropological-fraud/#50d9c1754d25|title=De Loys' Ape Was A Well Played Anthropological Fraud|accessdate=2017-06-30|author=David Bressan|archive-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520072440/https://www.forbes.com/sites/davidbressan/2016/01/31/de-loys-ape-was-a-well-played-anthropological-fraud/#50d9c1754d25|dead-url=no}}</ref>

